review: *** ** *** **** ******** ** ***** ***** The most professional and very sweet, down to earth and polite.  **** ************* *** ethical.  We were previously consulting Dr. Xyz at cloud nine and we changed to Dr Jnanashree and we felt the difference. I strongly recommend Dr. Jnanashree.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review: She is awesome. I liked the way she treat the patients with love and care. She gave good advice about my pregnancy. She clearly said about the do's and dont's during the first trimester of my pregnancy. Happy to meet her and very very happy the way she deals with all the queries that I asked her.

** ********** ** *** ** *** **** ******* * **** **** ******* * ****** ************* *** full of positivity! She put me so much at ease and made me feel very confident that I will be able to recover. She is a very ethical practitioner and does not prescibe unwanted tests. My family is so happy about how good I feel after visiting her! I totally recommend her for any gynaecological problems that one maybe facing!

Down to earth and very polite lady
 I'm always recommending her only in my society whenever I'm listening about pregnancy from my dear ones 
Ready to help her patient any time 

Myself DEEPIKA GOEL
It is very satisfactory experience all the times I have visited Dr. Jannashree. She is a very good Doctor and a good human being.
Its an complete saisfacsaisfatory appointment.... I  am soo happy to interact with Doctor.. I will recommend this to the needypeople compulsorily

review: ***** **** *** ****** Very Experienced, Calm soft spoken and Very Competent. She is abreast with the latest in her field.

I had been to hospital and it was for gynaecology related. ****** *** **** ** ********** *** I can surely recommend doctor to others. I had went for normal consultation. There was no waiting time in the hospital.
Ma'am was very nice and friendly. She patiently answered all my questions and gave me appropriate advice
